.umb-grid
	.grid-section
		.site--banner(data-js="site-banner", role="banner")
			.container
				.row
					.col-sm-12
						.site--banner-wrap
							img.site--banner-img.hidden(src="images/awm-banner-compact-bg.jpg", alt="Client Login", role="img")
							h1.site--banner-heading(role="heading")
								| Client Login
							p.site--banner-content
								| AFL Online offers a secure, confidential, convenient way for AFL clients to access their account and communicate with the AFL team. Clients may log on 24 hours a day, seven days a week to send &amp; receive mail, view balances, transaction history or statements, access AFL documentation, or read the latest investment commentary.
		.site--content
			.container
				.row
					.col-sm-12
						.site--content-wrap
							form.form-signin
								span#reauth-email.reauth-email
								input#inputEmail.form-control(type='email', placeholder='Email address', required='', autofocus='')
								input#inputPassword.form-control(type='password', placeholder='Password', required='')
								#remember.checkbox
									label
										input(type='checkbox', value='remember-me')
										|  Remember me
								button.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.btn-signin(type='submit') Sign in
							a.forgot-password(href='#')
								| Forgot the password?